      <title>汽车贷款裁决后英国银行面临数十亿美元的赔付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/uk-banks-facing-billions-more-in-payouts-after-auto-loan-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦一家法院作出裁决，称银行对汽车贷款客户不够透明，英国银行因此面临支付数十亿美元的额外赔偿金，此举导致银行股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/uk-banks-facing-billions-more-in-payouts-after-auto-loan-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 10:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
