    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《曼谷邮报》报道，泰国将把退休年龄提高至 65 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/thailand-will-raise-retirement-age-to-65-bangkok-post-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《曼谷邮报》报道，由于医疗保健和医疗技术的进步，泰国计划将私营部门和政府部门的退休年龄提高至 65 岁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/thailand-will-raise-retirement-age-to-65-bangkok-post-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 08:08:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对中国股市而言，刺激措施比美国大选更重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/stimulus-matters-more-than-us-election-for-chinese-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来已习惯中美贸易争端的投资者似乎愿意冒着美国总统大选后关税进一步上调的风险，并青睐中国资产，押注美国将出台更多刺激措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/stimulus-matters-more-than-us-election-for-chinese-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
